node.title: Woman found with gunshot wound in west Auckland
node.description: Police are investigating after a woman was found with a serious gunshot injury last night in New Lynn, west Auckland.
node.content:
["Police are investigating after a woman was found with a serious gunshot injury last night in New Lynn, west Auckland.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123rf.com\n
", "Police say they were called to an address in the suburb about 12am.", "The woman was taken to Auckland Hospital, where she remains in a critical condition.", "A 26-year-old male has been arrested and charged with unlawful possession of a firearm.", "Police said he was helping them with ongoing inquiries and they were not looking for anyone else in relation to the incident."]
